条件相对较好，它们比较高，也很亮，肉眼可见。要想看到暗弱的天王星，则需要借助望远镜。随着太阳西沉，水星、土星、海王星的高度比较低，观测难度比较大。海王星的亮度只有8等左右，在昏光中即使用望远镜也很难被观测到。“七星连珠”月底上演靠谱吗？北京天文馆专家解答 - 新京报"},"attached_info":"CkII3om+trjAnqtJEAMaCTExMzE2NDA4OSDxyPC8BjAAOI8BQBhyCzEwOTQwMjAyMDk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1ed439ebdacc4f7771357fb166c67711_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"25_1740558190.915485","card_id":"Q_665169498","target":{"id":665169498,"title":"为何日本会大量废止长途卧铺列车?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665169498","type":"question","created":1724483255,"answer_count":29,"follower_count":76,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[229,1716,2883,24458,42486],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"日本与中国皆为高铁大国，可谓高铁密度极大，近代中国虽有普速列车减少之趋势，但不若日本几乎欲废止殆尽之势；相反中国之巴士客运行业却逐渐殆尽，而日本巴士客运业却逐渐成长发达，以上原因终究是为何呢？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I3om+trjAnqtJEAMaCTExMDA5MzA0MiC3jaa2BjAAOExAGXIJNjY1MTY5NDk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9c1dfbf82297d48b9b31f30fe4ac02b3_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"26_1740558190.915927","card_id":"Q_5703257394","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":5703257394,"title":"最近上班感觉越来越没意思，后面还有二三十年要上班，该怎么办呢？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5703257394","type":"question","created":1733100332,"answer_count":613,"follower_count":1519,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[25